{"tid":1607767,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣中華統促黨總裁張安樂挺韓　倡陸「克里米亞模式」吞台","createTime":"2019-10-01T03:52:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T04:09:52.000Z","uid":46356,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4156a45bdb2fd69c08d0a253de347ae17ece15f5","tid":1607767,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:52:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20190930/AV2P4E3DJHN6Y4YX7OLGVS2TCY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20190930%2FAV2P4E3DJHN6Y4YX7OLGVS2TCY%2F&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdUigq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=c9569105\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20190930%2FAV2P4E3DJHN6Y4YX7OLGVS2TCY%2F&h=80f5d15e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20190930/AV2P4E3DJHN6Y4YX7OLGVS2TCY/</a><br />\n白狼挺韓 倡陸「克里米亞模式」吞台<br />\n更新時間 (HKT): 2019.10.01 02:20<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/H4X5uUU8UIixIMZDR0zxy4pPJq8=/190x119/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/NRYJTKWK5MLQVKBITM7TIAZ3WA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FH4X5uUU8UIixIMZDR0zxy4pPJq8%3D%2F190x119%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FNRYJTKWK5MLQVKBITM7TIAZ3WA.gif&h=6427aff1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張安樂稱大陸能用「克里米亞模式」統一台灣。<br />\n<br />\n綽號「白狼」、支持中共的台灣中華統促黨總裁張安樂表示，他支持韓國瑜當選下任總統，因韓當選可為兩岸帶來八年和平；而中國大陸在八年期間發展強大，美國不敢以武力干預台灣問題，大陸便可仿效俄國吞併克里米亞，以「克里米亞模式」統一台灣。克里米亞原屬烏克蘭，2014年被俄國武力吞併。<br />\n<br />\n收黑金做中共爛頭卒<br />\n<br />\n張安樂在fb上載一段影片，他在片中被俄媒問及2020總統大選時，表態支持韓國瑜上位，原因是韓當政可帶給兩岸八年和平，認為台灣會走「克里米亞模式」和中國統一。他形容俄羅斯收回克里米亞是「和平、沒有留一滴血」，當時美國不敢介入，「就是（俄國）總理講的一句話『美國人敢動，我讓你半個小時化為灰燼！』」<br />\n<br />\n白狼指，大陸在八年後的實力可與美國相提並論，美國不可能為台灣與中國拚命。「八年以後，相信中國大陸的戰略核武器可以跟美國保證互相毀滅，那個時候，美國不敢介入台灣問題」。事實上台灣內部早洞悉中共有意製造克里米亞翻版。國安局曾在今年5月指，中共正複製俄國吞併克里米亞模式，在台灣散播爭議性訊息。張安樂擁有台灣黑幫背景，同時身兼「統派」色彩的中華統一促進黨總裁。他曾被指涉嫌接受大陸獻金資助，在台組織犯罪活動，被控違反政治獻金法、偽造文書等罪。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"68afb046f9e8aa627fdf823fc23361251e1282da","tid":1607767,"uid":134323,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:55:17.000Z","msg":"倡美國可用苿莉花模式滅共"},{"pid":"29c372dcc97c802174659f265ba46724826e453c","tid":1607767,"uid":291835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:57:03.000Z","msg":"咪試下台灣公投囉, 我都好想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33ed381a42c2b4d90af05222bc5b157b318c4bf","tid":1607767,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:01:40.000Z","msg":"北佬"},{"pid":"4c428e6bba447612b269e534751a45af3f70d7e6","tid":1607767,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:03:08.000Z","msg":"又同蔡英文助攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce9964ce07981b758dc7792bc334f4c8e306eeb","tid":1607767,"uid":186997,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:04:31.000Z","msg":"呢個統促黨根本就係叛國組織嚟，唔明點解台灣政府仲唔取締咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd646b6fbfd8bd9e94378ba4945b939ac0c21ca7","tid":1607767,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68afb046f9e8aa627fdf823fc23361251e1282da","tid":1607767,"uid":134323,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:55:17.000Z","msg":"倡美國可用苿莉花模式滅共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:05:29.000Z","msg":"茉莉花好抽象"},{"pid":"455f686b16382e199af9abb24ab1918c8c1f78ed","tid":1607767,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:06:47.000Z","msg":"呢個党.....共狗黎"},{"pid":"26486f512cb62974af13d6a717369539439b8be7","tid":1607767,"uid":41116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T04:07:11.000Z","msg":"點解可以公然叫人入侵自己國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p